data.description: One of Harrison Counties finest locations off of blacktop road, close to town ! Lots of privacy on this 8.38 acres ! Timber and wildlife galore ! Home features 3 BR on main floor, formal DR, family room ,LR with wood burning insert fireplace ! Home has 1.75 BA. Newer kitchen , enclosed sun room, and front porch. Basement has been totally remodeled with 2 non conforming BR, large 3/4 BA, and huge family room. There is a 2 car attached garage and carport. There are also 2 more detached garages and work shops . You will want to check out this acreage right away, as it will go fast. Showings begin Thursday Nov. 30 after 4:15 pm
